\SE[3]We've come this far smoothly, haven't we? \!\SE[1]If
Vega is doing well, we might not even need any support in
the first place...

\SE[4]Well, umm... \SE[3]There are also people here who are
full of motivation, you know.

\SE[18]Don't worry so much, it'll be fine! After all, we
have Onee-sama with us! \SE[10]There's no way we'll lose to
such a pervert!

\SE[14]I came so that I wouldn't miss any cool moments of
Onee- sama!

\SE[68]Hmm, it's hard to gather everyone when there are so
many people.... \!\SE[3]Hey, Laura. Take command. You're the
oldest after all.

\SE[64]Me...!? \!\SE[5]No, it's true that if I don't do
it...

\SE[3]Alright, let's go save Nikita! \SE[1]Let's all work
together and do our best!!

\SE[2](Our morale has improved, but there are still
individual differences in leadership.... \SE[3] It's like a
picnic after all.)
